    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Project car / fixer-upper being sold in poor overall condition. This vehicle shows heavy wear inside and out, with noticeable cosmetic deterioration, deferred maintenance, and signs of age throughout. Expect visible flaws to the body, paint, and interior, and it should be assumed to need substantial mechanical attention as well. Best suited for someone looking for a restoration project, a budget beater with work, or a parts vehicle rather than a ready-to-drive daily car. Priced accordingly and being represented honestly for what it is.",
