    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Enthusiastic, honest classic with good bones and a presentable driver-quality look. This is a fair-condition example that still has plenty of charm, but it shows its age in places and will benefit from cosmetic refreshing and/or continued sorting depending on how nice you want to take it. A solid choice for someone who wants an approachable classic to enjoy now and improve over time.",
