    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Value-priced and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers an affordable entry point for a budget-minded buyer, handy commuter, or project opportunity. It presents honest wear consistent with age and use, and it stands out as a straightforward, low-cost option for someone who appreciates practicality over pretense. Priced to reflect its condition while still delivering real utility, this is a smart chance to secure dependable transportation at an accessible price.",
      "price": 5950.0,
