      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest budget-friendly option that could make a great daily beater, learner car, or little project. It\u2019s priced to reflect its condition and offers a lot of value for someone practical who doesn\u2019t mind a few rough edges. If you want something cheap, straightforward, and worth a look, this could be the one.",
      "price": 5800.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly project or parts-and-driver candidate with great enthusiast potential. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, the chassis feels fundamentally usable, and it has the kind of honest mechanical character that makes it worth saving. Not a showroom piece, but a straightforward platform for someone who wants an affordable entry point and doesn\u2019t mind cosmetic/mechanical cleanup. Priced to move for the next owner who knows what they\u2019re looking at.",
      "price": 4900.0,
